H.B. 1055
GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
Apr 27, 2026
SESSION 2025
HOUSE PRINCIPAL CLERK
H D
HOUSE BILL DRH10596-NGa-146
Short Title: GTCC Aviation Center Expansion. (Public)
Sponsors: Representative Clark.
Referred to:
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO APPROPRIATE FUNDS FOR THE EXPANSION OF THE GUILFORD
3 TECHNICAL COMMUNITY COLLEGE AVIATION CENTER.
4 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
5 SECTION 1. There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Community
6 Colleges System Office the sum of one million eight hundred thousand dollars ($1,800,000) in
7 nonrecurring funds for the 2026-2027 fiscal year to be allocated to Guilford Technical
8 Community College (GTCC) to support the expansion of the GTCC Aviation Center and for
9 capital expenses related to that expansion. Funds appropriated in this section shall not revert but
10 shall remain available until expended.
11 SECTION 2. This act becomes effective July 1, 2026.
*DRH10596-NGa-146*

